textBeforeTable: Those that won player of the year for their sport are noted in parenthesis. Scott Talbot won Coach of the Year for boys tennis and LaVerne Huston won Coach of the Year for volleyball. The fall sports all-conference teams for the Tri-Valley Conference were recently announced. All of Windsors fall sports teams except football are in the Tri-Valley Conference. The football team plays in the Northern Conference.
